(text "NOTE: no wires used - connectivity is via matching label names (valid KiCad practice)." (at 20.32 219.71 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid c8480d74-3ba8-4840-aac2-8986bff2e19f))
(text "The real pack already has a protection-only BMS; U1/Q1/Q2 are optional/DNP unless a bare-cell pack is used." (at 20.32 226.06 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 9493abbc-8df3-4005-bfab-250330d007a6))
(text "RS1 remains populated as the BQ34Z100-G1 low-side current shunt; Kelvin route SRP/SRN per TI layout guidance." (at 20.32 232.41 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 088014a5-d429-460e-842a-0ce66092db52))
(text "U10 pinout is verified against TI Table 5-1; divider 215k/16.5k gives about 0.90V at 12.6V full-charge 3S." (at 20.32 237.49 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 2972bec1-7808-41c7-953c-aaf7fc443c64))
(text "TS1/TS2/TS3/FG_TS use independent thermistor dividers per-IC (not shared) per design decision." (at 20.32 243.84 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid de29a421-5346-4445-83de-75ef2a114d02))
(text "Charger I2C/INT/QON/CE pull-ups use MCU_3V3 so STM32 pins never see REGN-level logic." (at 20.32 250.19 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 797156cb-ca0f-4066-8666-d867587b27e2))
(text "U2 ILIM_HIZ divider sets about 3A input-current clamp from REGN; PROG selects 3S/1.5MHz POR defaults." (at 20.32 256.54 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 954d542d-43d2-49a2-986c-4c95ba3290ab))
(text "J190 is shared: default random-DC mode populates D191 to U2; solar mode populates D8/U3 MPPT option." (at 20.32 264.16 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid d4efe866-b6a3-4b51-bfba-c76856a6a8c4))
(text "If solar option is used, U3 starts at 18V nominal MPP, 12.6V 3S regulation, and 1A solar charge current." (at 20.32 271.78 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 6da66c86-abcb-412a-a603-f28ffe53d23f))
(text "Default BOM should not populate D8 with D191; choose random-DC charger input or solar MPPT behavior for J190." (at 20.32 279.4 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid da556f20-e24f-4e40-841c-98fbcd4e6530))
(text "AUX_DC_ADC lets EC firmware detect random bench/DC inputs and reduce BQ25798 input current if the source droops." (at 20.32 287.02 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid f97c7daf-80b2-4b33-94a7-94c257c9715c))
(text "U2 VAC1/VAC2 tie to VBUS_COMBINED in no-external-mux mode; ACDRV1/2 go to GND." (at 20.32 294.64 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 483cf6c2-beeb-4e21-a1f4-34574ff72cd8))
(text "SDRV has 1nF to GND because the ship FET is unused in this first integrated laptop spin." (at 20.32 302.26 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid c7b2d87f-2234-4540-a47a-3f9746efd2eb))
(text "DNP Q1/Q2 candidate: Infineon IPD90N04S4L-04, 40V 3.8mR DPAK, active/preferred, pin 1=G 2=D/tab 3=S." (at 20.32 309.88 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 3559fe28-53de-4abe-9eb2-5bbd19b8d22e))
(text "DNP Q3/Q4 candidate: Infineon IPD50N04S4L-08, 40V 7.3mR DPAK, lower Qg for BQ24650 6V gate drive." (at 20.32 317.5 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 65603332-d3d2-411e-acd9-4e3351c3fc92))
